Title: Stack Overflow Podcast #104 - Jenn Schiffer Talks to Us about Fog Creek's New Glitch
Description: On this week's episode, Jenn Schiffer - aka jennmoneydollars - talks to us about joining Fog Creek as the company's new Community Engineer. She'll be focused on their brand new community, Glitch, which launched today. The gang also listens to Joel rant a lot about a shack he owns.
